## \f3\u-10179?\u-8480?\f0  TEKNOLOJ\f1\u304? STACK\par
\par
### Frontend\par
- **HTML5** - Semantic markup\par
- **Vanilla JavaScript (ES6+)** - Framework-free, derleme gerektirmeyen\par
- **Tailwind CSS** - Utility-first CSS framework (CDN)\par
- **Font Awesome 6.5.0** - \u304?konlar\par
- **Plus Jakarta Sans / Inter / Space Grotesk** - Google Fonts\par
- **SweetAlert2** - Modern alert/modal\par
- **Chart.js** - Grafikler (D\f0\'f6viz/Alt\f1\u305?n, Analytics)\par
\par
### Backend & Database\par
- **Supabase** - PostgreSQL veritaban\u305?\par
  - Authentication (Email/Password)\par
  - Row Level Security (RLS)\par
  - Realtime Subscriptions\par
  - Storage (gelecekte)\par
  - Edge Functions (Deno)\par
- **PostgreSQL** - \u304?li\'bakisel veritaban\u305?\par
\par
### Harita & Konum\par
- **Google Maps JavaScript API** - Harita g\f0\'f6rselle\f1\'batirme\par
- **Google Distance Matrix API** - Mesafe hesaplama\par
- **Leaflet.js** - Alternatif harita k\f0\'fct\'fcphanesi (S\f1\u305?la Yolu)\par
- **Nominatim OpenStreetMap API** - Geocoding\par
- **Browser Geolocation API** - Kullan\u305?c\u305? konumu\par
\par
### Harici API'ler\par
- **NewsAPI** - Otomatik haber \f0\'f6nerileri (100 req/g\'fcn \'fccretsiz)\par
- **ExchangeRate-API** - D\'f6viz kurlar\f1\u305?\par
- **Frankfurter API** - Tarihsel d\f0\'f6viz verileri\par
- **Travelpayouts API** - U\'e7ak bileti f\f1\u305?rsatlar\u305? (yap\u305?land\u305?rma gerekli)\par
- **Booking.com Deals API** - Otel promosyonlar\u305? (yap\u305?land\u305?rma gerekli)\par
- **Adzuna API** - \u304?\'ba ilanlar\u305? (admin paneli)\par
- **Rentalcars.com** - Ara\f0\'e7 kiralama affiliate\par
- **Supabase Edge Functions** - Backend proxy (alt\f1\u305?n fiyatlar\u305?, CORS bypass)\par
\par
### PWA & Mobil\par
- **Progressive Web App (PWA)** - manifest.json + service-worker.js\par
- **Capacitor** - Native mobil d\f0\'f6n\'fc\f1\'ba\f0\'fcm i\'e7in haz\f1\u305?r (capacitor.config.json)\par
- **Service Worker** - Offline destek, cache y\f0\'f6netimi\par
\par
### Hosting & CDN\par
- **Netlify** - Statik hosting\par
- **CDN** - Tailwind, Font Awesome, Supabase JS (CDN \'fczerinden)\par
